
{ convert mp4 to mp3

code {
ffmpeg -i file.mp4 file.mp3
code }

}

{ Print duration of an mp3 #duration

code {
ffmpeg -i Multiverse/Mutliverse.mp3  2>&1 | grep Duration
code }

Compare with → tools/mp3info#duration[mp3info].

}

